comment: Beal (WAS) maintains legal guarding position on Ross (ORL) on the perimeter.
Ross (ORL) clamps Beal's (WAS) arm and affects his shot attempt in transition.
Porter Jr. (WAS) makes contact to Biyombo's (ORL) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Ross (ORL) and Morris (WAS) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Gordon (ORL) makes marginal contact with Bogdanovic (WAS) during the loose ball.
Payton (ORL) makes incidental contact with Wall (WAS) that does not affect his SQBR.
[Observable in enhanced video] Fournier (ORL) moves his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Morris (WAS) makes contact to Fournier's (ORL) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Payton (ORL) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Wall (WAS) that does not affect his SQBR on the drive to the basket.
Wall (WAS) maintains legal guarding position and blocks the shot attempt by Gordon (ORL).
Bogdanovic (WAS) maintains legal guarding position on Gordon's (ORL) shot attempt in transition.
